export default function Stars({star}) {

    return (
        <svg 
            className={`${star} star`} 
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" 
            viewBox="0 0 40 40">
            <g 
                mask="url(#icon-star-a)" 
                fill-rule="evenodd">
                <rect 
                    fill="#E2E5EA" 
                    x="0" 
                    y="0" 
                    width="40" 
                    height="38">
                </rect>
                <rect 
                    x="0" 
                    y="0" 
                    width="40" 
                    height="38">
                </rect>
            </g>
        </svg>
    )
}
